AKURE – No fewer than 50 people have been at St Francis Catholic Church, Owo, Owo Local Government Area of Ondo State during the service by some gunmen who invaded the shooting the worshippers sporadically. The gunmen invaded the church which is bwhind Olowo’s palace near Mega School at Owaluwa, area of Owo. They launched dynamites into the church while they shot every worshipper who escaped from the church. -Advertisement- Sources revealed that the parish priest was abducted by the gunmen and escaped from the scene. Details later